/04/21214504/Screen-Shot-2015-06-15-at-1.56.22-PM.png" alt=3D"Graph of 1-e^=
(-0.5x * e) with shaded region showing probability that x &lt; 0.3935" widt=
h=3D"385" height=3D"215"></a></div>
</li>
