frac"><span class=3D"mrow"><span class=3D"mi">l</span><span class=3D"mi">n<=
/span><span class=3D"mrow"><span class=3D"mo">(</span><span class=3D"mrow">=
<span class=3D"mn">0.30</span></span><span class=3D"mo">)</span></span></sp=
an><span class=3D"mrow"><span class=3D"mo">=E2=80=93</span><span class=3D"m=
